<div class="container container-top">
  <h1 class="text-lg">Resend Confirmation</h1>
  <p>Unfortunately, sometimes our mails are sent into the spam folder. SPAM FOLDER!!! Do we look like people who would spam? But the world is a rough for the e-postman, so we let it go by. Please enter your eMail below to get the eMail confirmation link again. Please look in the spam folder if you don't get it this time also. Sorry about this; we promise to deliver ham. 100% vegan ham! ;)</p>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-offset-4 col-lg-4 col-md-offset-4 col-md-4 col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-offset-2 col-xs-8">
      <%= simple_form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: confirmation_path(resource_name), html: { method: :post }) do |f| %>
      <div class="panel panel-primary">
        <div class="panel-heading">Resend Confirmation</div>
        <div class="panel-body">
          <%= f.error_notification %>
          <%= f.full_error :confirmation_token %>
          <%= f.input :email, autofocus: true %>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-footer">
          <%= f.button :submit, "Resend", :class => "btn btn-primary", :title => 'Press to get eMail confirmation link'%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%= render "devise/shared/links" %>